HEADWORD: Recussion
<hw>Re*cus"sion</hw> <pr>(r?*k?sh"?n)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[L.
<ets>recutire</ets>, <ets>recussum</ets>, to beat back; pref.
<ets>re-</ets> re- + <ets>quatere</ets> to shake.]</ety> <def>The act of
beating or striking back.</def>⟦br⟧
